  "prompt": "How can I arrange a personal counselling session with Tanmoy Ray?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, Tanmoy Ray is known for providing career counseling, particularly in the areas of higher education, studying abroad, and professional development. Here are some steps you can take to arrange a personal counseling session with him:\n\n1. **Website:** Check Tanmoy Ray's official website or professional profile pages to see if there is an option to book a session or contact him directly.\n\n2. **Email:** If there is an email address provided on his site or profile, you can write a detailed email explaining your needs and request for a counseling session.\n\n3. **Social Media:** Follow Tanmoy Ray on social media platforms such as LinkedIn, Twitter, or other professional networks where he might be active. You might be able to send him a direct message to request a session.\n\n4. **Educational Consultancies:** Tanmoy Ray collaborates with various educational consultancies and organizations. Research if he is affiliated with any such organizations, and reach out to them for scheduling a session.\n\n5. **Online Platforms:** Search for Tanmoy Ray on online counseling platforms or professional advice websites where he might offer his services.\n\nRemember to provide clear details about what you hope to achieve from the counseling session, as this will help him understand your requirements better.",
